    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto\nLand lease issued to one person and mentioning the usual condition that the lessee has to pay his taxes according to the instalments of the sultan (l. 4) and that if he cultivates more he has to pay for it (l. 6). The contract ends with the wish that the lessee will sow with God\u00b4s blessing.\n\u00a0\nVerso\nEnd of debt acknowledgement containing the usual formulae (l. 1). The end is marked by the phrase that the document was read to the parties preceding the witness statements (l. 3). Of the date only the month (l. 4) is preserved."
    },
